  "title": "Room Attendant",
  "description": "<p>5 Days Work (Rotating Shifts)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Clean and maintain apartment room cleanliness and other areas of responsibility according to SOP.</p>\n<p>- Complete 15 Credits quota assigned</p>\n<p>- Replenish guest supplies and ensure that guests requests are promptly attended to</p>\n<p>- Report damage or malfunction in apartment rooms /areas to Supervisor</p>\n<p>- Maintain cleaning equipment in a proper state of cleanliness</p>\n<p>- Reports lost and found articles to the Supervisor</p>\n<p>- Deliver guest request items / guest laundry</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- **Attractive Bonus**</p>\n<p>- **AWS provided**</p>\n<p>- **Meal Allowance**</p>\n<p>- **Yearly Increment**</p>\n<p>-**Medical Insurance**</p>\n<p>-**Attractive Package**</p>",
